### Title Tag Rules

| Rule | Requirement |
|------|-------------|
| Length | 50-60 characters (Google truncates at ~60) |
| Format | Primary Keyword | Secondary | Brand |
| Uniqueness | Every page MUST have unique title |
| Keyword placement | Primary keyword within first 3 words |
| No keyword stuffing | Natural language, readable |

### Meta Description Rules

| Rule | Requirement |
|------|-------------|
| Length | 150-160 characters |
| Include | Primary keyword, value proposition, CTA |
