|--------|----------------|
| Experience | Include case studies, patient testimonials (anonymized), practitioner insights |
| Expertise | Author bios with credentials, degrees, certifications, years of experience |
| Authoritativeness | Cite reputable sources (NIH, APA, peer reviewed), link to credentials |
| Trustworthiness | Clear disclaimers, last updated dates, contact info, privacy policy |

