## 10. Forbidden Practices

### SEO Violations
- Duplicate title tags across pages
- Missing or duplicate meta descriptions
- Keyword stuffing
- Hidden text or links
- Doorway pages
- Cloaking (showing different content to bots)
- Link schemes or purchased links
- Thin content (under 300 words for service pages)
- Missing canonical tags
- Orphan pages (no internal links)

### Schema Violations
- Schema that doesn't match visible content
- Fake reviews or ratings
- Fabricated credentials
- Missing required properties
- Using deprecated schema types

### Tracking Violations
- Loading tracking scripts before consent
- Missing event deduplication
- Tracking PII without hashing
- Missing consent records
- Double counting conversions

### E-E-A-T Violations
- Medical claims without sources
- Missing author attribution on YMYL content
- Outdated medical information
- No medical disclaimer
- Anonymous health advice

