### Outbound Link Implementation

```tsx
// External links MUST have rel="noopener" and target="_blank"
<a 
  href="https://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/topics/anxiety-disorders" 
  rel="noopener noreferrer"
  target="_blank"
>
  Learn more about anxiety disorders (NIMH)
</a>

